## To Do tasks UI:
	Suite requires data: Two existing tasks.
	
	Create a task
	Create a task, while a task is being edited
	Create a task, while a task is being created (i.e. just click the 'New' button - should just clear inputs)
	
	Edit a task
	Edit a task, while a task is being created
	Edit the same task, while a task is being edited (i.e. just click the same task - nothing should change)
	Edit a different task, while a task is being edited.

	Remove a task
	Remove a task, while a task is being created
	Remove a task, while a different task is being edited
	Remove a task, while that same task is being edited (the edit screen should close)

	